user_titlec: The Kebab Special and Shawar Special are not special at all.
user_comment: I had ordered the Kebab Special and Shawar Special to try them both for myself. First of all, putting a whole lot more ingredients into an item and increasing its price does not make it "special". The sauce was very runny/watery, and unbalance, there was no sweetness to it, so it delivered this 'weird' taste as you keep eating it. The chicken meat was bland and dry, all I could taste was pepper. I did not even get my french fries as in my order. The packaging totally failed because of the runny sauce. When the food arrived, they were not hot, not even lukewarm. I am reviewing it here as there are places out there, even at Nha Trang, that sell similiar products with better quality and at a much lower price. Just want to let the people, who have not had anything similar to this and think this is great, know. Or, as an honest comment/ criticism for the merchant to improve their products. My total bill was 148k vnd excluding shipping fee, I felt like I got scammed.

user_titlec: The Best Restaurant at Nha Trang
user_comment: An excellent and cozy place is most similar to Italy in all of Nha Trang, both in the kitchen and in the presence of its charm in the interior of the restaurant. The service and service is very professional, dishes are prepared and served faster than in many restaurants. The meat board was really waited once for a long time, but the meat is not quickly roasted and, besides, the portion is quite large), so keep in mind if you want to try the steak, order some salad in advance) a huge selection of pizzas, pasta carbonara and sickness just disappeared) for good New Year discounts, depending on the amount of the order they give a free bottle of alcohol. A nice bonus if you sit in a company, and for the purposes of the evening it was a little to drink and relax)

Loved this restaurant for its comfort and delicious cuisine. Even in Italy, such pasta is not cooked so tasty everywhere, not to mention pizza)) It is simply amazing, the dough is not dry, there are many fillings. And I almost forgot about the service, the guys work quickly and harmoniously, the dishes are brought out quickly and to everyone at once, which also leaves a pleasant imprint !!! Thank you very much! I will recommend to friends

Loved the restaurant. Spacious interior, which allows you to not sit back to back with other tables, which often happens in other places. A varied menu with large pictures - you know what you order. As for the taste of the dishes themselves, it is very difficult to speak, I want to eat, eat and eat. Incredibly delicious! Pasta, soup, pizza. There is no better place for Italian cuisine in Nha Trang. Come in, you will not regret.

Wonderful place! I liked the interior and the opportunity to choose between delicious seafood dishes and Italian cuisine. If you are a company of three or more people, take a pizza assorted, huge, and each piece carries a different filling, conveniently and creatively, in each piece of pizza a combination of shrimp, meat, pineapples and salmon pieces, to choose from! ) Pasta carbonara served in the original recipe with egg yolk in the middle of the plate, this has not been met for a long time. The price tag is adequate. We were ready to pay for such a service and cuisine more, but when they brought the bill, we liked this restaurant even more!
